  // ...
}
```

The bcycle test does NOT call `getVersionManifest()` or `getSystemPricingPlans()` or `getFreeBikeStatus()`. Wait, actually it calls `getSystemPricingPlans()` - no, it doesn't! The bcycle test block doesn't include `getSystemPricingPlans()`. Let me re-read:

```kotlin
context(service) {
  assertTrue(client.getSystemInformation().isSuccess)
  assertTrue(client.getStationInformation().isSuccess)
  assertTrue(client.getStationStatus().isSuccess)
